(393, 1, '2024-03-20 03:27:12', '2024-03-20 03:27:12', '[et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_image=\"https://www.menegotto.design/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/pexels-arturas-kokorevas-15521508-copy-scaled.jpg\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.menegotto.design/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/89414f71-0f11-4446-b4f1-95de0d658375.jpg\" title_text=\"89414f71-0f11-4446-b4f1-95de0d658375\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" border_radii=\"on|100px|100px|100px|100px\" border_width_all=\"14px\" border_color_all=\"#ffffff\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" custom_padding=\"|57px||||\" align=\"right\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Abril Fatface||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"20px\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Abril Fatface||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"57px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p>José Scaglione</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Abel||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"21px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p>A graphic designer, typeface designer, and co-founder of the independent type foundry<span> </span><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/foundries/typetogether\">TypeTogether</a><span> </span>with<span> </span><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/designers/veronika-burian\">Veronika Burian</a>, where they have published numerous award-winning type families. He teaches typography at the University of Buenos Aires, Argentina, and is frequently invited to lecture about typography and to lead workshops on typeface design at international conferences and academic institutions. José co-authored the book Cómo Crear Tipografías: Del Boceto a la Pantalla, and collaborated with Jorge de Buen Unna on his book Introducción al Estudio de la Tipografía.</p>\n<p>In 2012 José acted as chairman of the Letter.2 type design competition and conference. In 2013 he was appointed president of the Association Typographique Internationale (ATypI).</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Abril Fatface||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"57px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p>Veronika Burian</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Abel||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"21px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p>Veronika Burian studied Industrial Design in Munich and worked in that capacity in Vienna and Milan over a few years. Discovering her true passion for type, she graduated in 2003 with distinction from the MA in Typeface Design course in Reading, UK. Veronika then worked as a type designer at<span> </span><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/foundries/dalton-maag\">Dalton Maag</a><span> </span>in London for a few years, spent some time in Boulder, USA, and then her hometown, Prague, and is now enjoying life in sunny Cataluña, Spain.</p>\n<p>Veronika Burian is a type designer and the co-founder of the independent type foundry<span> </span><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/foundries/typetogether\">TypeTogether</a><span> </span>with<span> </span><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/designers/jose-scaglione\">José Scaglione</a>, publishing award-winning typefaces and collaborating on tailored typefaces for a variety of clients. She is also involved with Alphabettes.org, a showcase for work and research on lettering, typography, and type design by women, and she continues to give lectures and workshops at international conferences and universities.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.menegotto.design/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8f3a50ed-82b9-4e49-baa0-bac426731b99.jpg\" title_text=\"8f3a50ed-82b9-4e49-baa0-bac426731b99\" _builder_version=\"4.24.2\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" border_radii=\"on|100px|100px|100px|100px\" border_color_all=\"#ffffff\" border_width_all=\"15px\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Creators', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'creators', '', '', '2024-03-26 02:52:25', '2024-03-26 02:52:25', '', 0, 'https://www.menegotto.design/?page_id=393', 0, 'page', '', 0),
